args: {player_name}, we got trouble!\nA bunch'a fiends are headin' toward\na nearby village!
There's a whole boatload of 'em, too! \nWe're gonna have to do somethin'!
There's so many of them...\nWait, are they dead?
This one's a goner... And this one...\nLooks like someone got 'em before we did.
Each one was finished off with a single\narrow. This is the work of a professional.
He felled it in one strike. Was he the one\nwho took out the others?
That was amazin'... And that fiend was\nno slouch, either!
Don't gotta tell me that twice!\nBut that guy...
He ain't missed a single shot...
We can't just stand back and let him do all\nthe work. We need to go hel—
He took them all out by himself.
Heh. There's some pretty nutty folks in\nthis big ol' world, huh?
Maybe we should go say hi.\n...Hey there, buddy!
So you finally show yourselves.\nWhat do you want?
Eh, nothin' much. Just impressed by yer\nlittle archery show, is all.
I don't know that I've ever seen something\nquite like that before, even in the capital.
Oh, we ain't introduced ourselves yet,\nhave we? I'm Ranzal—just yer average\neveryday mercenary.
And this here's Prince\n{player_name} of Alberia.
I'm sorry, do you know me?
By name only. I am Hawk—a hunter.
It's nice to meet you, Hawk.
Your skills with a bow are impressive.\nI don't know how you hit those speedy\nfiends without missing a shot.
All creatures give a sign when they are\nready to move. Eyes, legs, muscles...
Observe those carefully, and perfect\naccuracy is no challenge.
Then what do you say about making use\nof those skills yourself?
Make me one of your companions.
Oh, of course! We'd love to have you!
Hang on just a sec here! Ya sure about\nthis, {player_name}?!\n
Why not, Ranzal? You saw what he can do.
(A hunter called Hawk... He can't actually\nbe the Reaper, right? ...Right?)
